{"tid":1989372,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(中美洲手足) 台灣邦交國貝里斯國民於廣州聲援香港示威被捕","createTime":"2020-04-26T02:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T02:54:06.000Z","uid":82640,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"558f1d3d556c03b10351829aadd778b55efdbaa0","tid":1989372,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T02:07:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">China to prosecute first foreign national over Hong Kong protests<br />\n中國起訴首名聲援香港示威的外國人<br />\n</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/apr/24/china-prosecute-first-foreign-national-hong-kong-protests\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2020%2Fapr%2F24%2Fchina-prosecute-first-foreign-national-hong-kong-protests&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnChVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=d90177f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/apr/24/china-prosecute-first-foreign-national-hong-kong-protests</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Belizean national 貝里斯國民</strong> Lee Henley Hu Xiang accused of &lsquo;colluding with foreign anti-China forces&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\nChina is prosecuting its first foreign national for involvement in the Hong Kong protests, which racked the city for much of last year.<br />\n<br />\nState media said on Friday that Guangzhou city&rsquo;s national security bureau had finished investigations into Lee Henley Hu Xiang, a Belizean national and Taiwan resident, and his case had been transferred to the Guangzhou people&rsquo;s procuratorate for prosecution.<br />\n<br />\nLee&rsquo;s case is the first prosecution of a foreigner in relation to the protests, <strong>but more than 7,000 citizens, mostly young Hong Kongers, have been charged or prosecuted. 世人無忘記香港有超過7千示威者被捕</strong><br />\n<br />\n中共開始全世界清算行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係想放灰或情緒勒索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而事實上香港人近日示威聲勢減弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連聲援香港嘅外國人都準備俾人清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人收皮唔係香港人收皮咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係成個自由世界崩潰㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日叫外國人撐我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我地做好本份未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人絕不可以累街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0d924cdf18915a768bcaf72c03987d046b2f0b","tid":1989372,"uid":214672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T02:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7877966c34280637b4ba08fd7be56baa01e05f6b","tid":1989372,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T02:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kRcwmHB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkRcwmHB.png&h=202e98ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"325eb8a025e69f46d3f0531d0e357c9da0e6cccb","tid":1989372,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7877966c34280637b4ba08fd7be56baa01e05f6b","tid":1989372,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T02:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kRcwmHB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkRcwmHB.png&h=202e98ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T02:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgm